snippet.title: 88 In 1 Space War ( Same As Gun-Nac NES) 4,617,620 pts. Shawne Vinson
snippet.description: Shawne Vinson (Me) enjoying the interactive video game controller system with 88 games in 1 as like plug and play system, and performing the highest score record with no continues for Space War (Same as different for Gun-Nac on NES)
